        "id": 1002539
      },
      "writtenOn": "2020-08-25T22:27:16Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Other ID tokens sometimes have `name` and `picture` fields with user\u0027s full name and profile picture. They can go into corresponding auth.User fields. Do ID tokens from IAP have them? See also https://chromium.googlesource.com/infra/luci/luci-go/+/refs/heads/master/server/auth/openid/user.go#53",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 96,
        "startChar": 1,
        "endLine": 99,
        "endChar": 2
      },
      "revId": "90c717b8a3a9a7fa4be8e1afe1359025256c428b",
