      "author": {
        "id": 1121710
      },
      "writtenOn": "2020-08-25T23:04:04Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "IAP only includes those two claims in signed headers to identify users, according to docs: https://cloud.google.com/iap/docs/signed-headers-howto#retrieving_the_user_identity\n\nThere might be a way to get that information with some other API, but I haven\u0027t looked into that yet.",
      "parentUuid": "77e81a79_a4b741e4",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 96,
        "startChar": 1,
        "endLine": 99,
